- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper proposes a heuristic algorithm for optimizing the transmission of heterogeneous traffic.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with the transmission of different types of data, including multimedia.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may touch upon security concerns related to the transmission of different types of data.
